The Ground Truth;;79;;88;;R;;Filmmaker Patricia Foulkrod examines the experiences of Iraq War veterans and the plight of the military. She documents stories of human wreckage arising from the horrors of war and military training dehumanizing soldiers. Approximately 10 veterans discuss how their time in Iraq changed their lives irrevocably .;;Documentary;;Patricia Foulkrod;;2006;;Robert Acosta,Kelly Dougherty,Sean Huze;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_ground_truth